Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.74,0:00:01.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darkness and Light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.91,0:00:03.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Into the chaos of\nthe Feudal Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.61,0:00:05.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel brings a\n{\i1}group of strangers together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:09.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}500 years across time,\ntheir destinies are controlled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:11.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the few remaining shards\nof the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:13.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feudal Fairy Tale:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:14.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:16.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The demon graveyard,\nwhere Inuyasha's father also sleeps,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:18.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}is the border between this\nworld and the next.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:20.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In order to obtain that last\nremaining Sacred Jewel shard,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:24.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}once again, we must find\nthe path that leads to that graveyard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:05.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That place that the river otter's\nfather {\i1}saw....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:09.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if Hakudoshi\nalready knows about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:11.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:13.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But where is this place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:15.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that's covered in white mist\nand strewn with giant bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:19.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I may've been there once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:23.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha is thinking the same thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:31.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}White mist and giant bones...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:35.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The border between this world\nand the next...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:40.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The grave of Inuyasha's father...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:00.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:05.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.\NI've been here before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:19.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Father....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:26.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:29.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're happy, Tetsusaiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:33.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I suppose {\i1}so....{\i0} It's been a long time\nsince you've seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:38.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Father, I've been using\NTetsusaiga to its fullest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:53.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:03.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:07.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The border between this\nworld and the next...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:10.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's where the\nlast shard is,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:12.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}then that's where I'll go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:22.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He wants me to\nvisit his grave, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:28.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where could Inuyasha have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:31.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe he went in\nsearch of Old Myoga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:32.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old Myoga?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:35.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How'll he find such\na teeny-tiny one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:39.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:44.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But why would he be\nlooking for Myoga?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:46.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:48.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but it's probably\nregarding the black pearl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:50.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Black pearl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:05:00.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! You there, Totosai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:02.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Totosai!\NYou're there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:04.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:08.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you want,\nshowing up so unexpectedly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:12.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't have business\nwith you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:14.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's Old Myoga?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:16.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are always so rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:26.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since you've actually\ncome looking for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:28.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it must be something\ntroublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:33.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This black pearl is the entryway
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:38.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to Inuyasha's father's grave\nand the border?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:39.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:46.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha's Tetsusaiga was to be\nfound at his father's grave.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:50.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}When we went to get\nthe sword,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}a space opened up\nfrom the black pearl{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}which connected to\nthe other world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:00.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Sesshomaru's\nat the grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:14.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}After he took possession\nof Tetsusaiga,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:16.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}we returned to this world...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:31.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But the black pearl fell back\ninto Inuyasha's right eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:32.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:37.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see, a way to remove the\nblack pearl from your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:39.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's a way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:41.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:45.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When the black pearl allowed you\npassage into the other world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:46.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it served its purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:50.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, it has become a part\nof your eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and it no longer has\ndemon power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:54.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't use it anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:55.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, you cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:58.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then how do I get\nto my old man's grave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:00.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your father's grave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:01.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:04.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good! Good boy, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:07.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you've finally realized how\ngreat your father was
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:10.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and decided to pay your respects\nat his grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:13.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you ever hit\nme like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:17.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You always hit me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:19.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a surprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:23.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that you're showing\nsuch respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:25.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! It's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:29.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The last Sacred Jewel shard\nmay be found there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:31.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In order to get it before Naraku,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:33.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we have to go ourselves\nand beat him to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:35.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel shard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:38.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we can't use the black pearl,\nany other method will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:41.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How can I get to\nthe other world?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:43.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:51.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:53.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who're you calling "stupid"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:56.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Think hard for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:08:00.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That demon graveyard is\nin a separate world,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:02.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,reached only by\ntraveling through a special path.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:06.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How could a Sacred Jewel shard\nhave gotten there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:08.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's right, Master Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:13.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And besides, Kagome was\nwith you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:18.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yet she didn't sense a Sacred\NJewel shard at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:20.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-That was {\i1}then....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:22.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think it'd be the same\nthis time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:27.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup! Do you intend to\ntake me to the grave or not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:31.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In order to go to the graveyard,\nyou must see H-Hosenki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hosenki?\NWho the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:36.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An old friend of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:40.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hosenki cultivates many kinds\nof precious jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:45.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And each one of them can serve as\nan entryway to the demon graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.53,0:08:48.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0} So he made\NInuyasha's black pearl, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:49.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:52.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was given to Inuyasha's\nfather by Hosenki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:57.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demon graveyard is\nthe final resting place of the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:09:01.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is no place for the living\nto be visiting indiscriminately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:05.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If that's where the Sacred Jewel\nshard is, that's where we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That {\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}\NHe's finally making his move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:29.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've just about had it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:33.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How long must I baby-sit\nthis kid?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:38.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I kill him right here and now,\NI'll be free...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:40.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:44.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagura....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:49.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know your thoughts\nlike the back of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:53.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You shouldn't think\nfoolish thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:02.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right, I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:07.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn kid!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:21.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:26.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru,\nwhere are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:31.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My lord! Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:34.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:37.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then who should I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You, A-un?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:45.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It couldn't be Rin, could it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:48.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That kid's scent...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:52.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and this scent that\NI smell beyond him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:54.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:57.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And this time, for {\i1}sure....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:10:59.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:02.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:06.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master {\i1}Jaken....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Better not ask him\nunnecessary questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:11.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or else, he said that\nhe'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:13.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:15.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:18.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How much further, Myoga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:19.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:21.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Once we pass this valley,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:24.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we'll reach the marsh where\NHosenki lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:28.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sun's almost setting\nand we're still not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:32.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Would you like to rest\naround here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:37.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Like we have\nthe luxury to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:42.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:47.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As always, he sure has\na lot of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:12:01.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Inuyasha,\nthis is impossible, even for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's wait for Kirara.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:05.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:09.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If anything stands in my way,\NI'll just blast it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:14.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:17.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:24.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:26.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are amazing, Master Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:28.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew you could do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:29.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:34.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:40.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is so reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:42.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:46.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, keep at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:48.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}O-Okay....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:57.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}W- What...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:01.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:05.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hakudoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were careless,\NInuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:29.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you came up ahead\nof us and waited for this moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:33.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Go right ahead\nand attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:37.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I'm not gonna\ndie so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:39.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no intention\nof killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:42.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see if
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:47.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you were going to make it\nto Hosenki's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:50.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit! You know about\NHosenki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's such a {\i1}shame....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:55.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't be able\nto see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.44,0:13:56.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:13:58.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:13:59.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're {\i1}not....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:02.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry needlessly,\NInuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:05.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't interfere\nwith you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:09.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After all, I don't want\nthe entertainment to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:10.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whaddya say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:14.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it,\NInuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:16.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You and your friends, or {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:20.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who will be the first to reach the\nborder between this world and the next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:22.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:28.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:34.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:34.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:37.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:41.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:43.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:55.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:00.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hosenki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:03.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hosenki!\NAren't you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:09.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hosenki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:11.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:28.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara, get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.51,0:15:38.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! It's you, Hosenki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:42.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:45.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are no jewels here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:49.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hosenki! It's me, Myoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:51.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:15:59.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:02.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Myoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:07.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's Hosenki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:10.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I am Hosenki's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:12.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hosenki is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:12.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:14.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Died?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:15.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}W-Who....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:17.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who killed him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:21.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, he died just recently\nfrom old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old age?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:27.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He died peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.66,0:16:31.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am Hosenki II.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:32.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:34.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You said earlier that there are no jewels\nthat can lead us to the grave...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:35.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:36.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:40.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My father used all the jewels\nbefore he passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:45.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I am in the process of\nmaking new jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:47.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then let us have those jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:50.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Inuyasha, at least\nsay, "please."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:53.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup! I'll take 'em by force\nif I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:54.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, {\i1}now....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:56.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This may not work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:58.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please, Master Hosenki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:00.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We really need those\nprecious jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:04.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I don't mind\ngiving them to {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:11.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you'll have to\nwait a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How long'll it take?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:15.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:19.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'd ya say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:22.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm still in training\nto master jewel-making.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:25.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demons sure have patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Perhaps this is futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:29.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:32.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't there any other way?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:34.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}While we're wasting\ntime here,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:39.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku or that kid Hakudoshi\ncould get the shard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:54.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And? Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:59.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The way to the border between\nthis world and the {\i1}next....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:01.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:04.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Although there's only one path\nat this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:05.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:08.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:11.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:14.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's only one way...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Break open the gate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:20.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Hakudoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:24.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm....interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:25.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:26.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:28.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:30.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Errand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:04.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The scent disappeared...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:07.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did I let him slip away?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:11.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err....Lord Sesshomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:15.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:17.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:26.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been so stressful\nfor me lately...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:27.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:32.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You should train and learn\nto turn your sighs into flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:35.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then there would be\nflowers everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:36.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:38.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:45.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! Please wait,\NLord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:53.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're at a dead-end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:54.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:56.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't wait a hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:01.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Myoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:04.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't know\nany other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.21,0:20:08.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! There is no other way\nto reach the graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:10.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wanna {\i1}know....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:13.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,where the entrance is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:18.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:22.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hakudoshi is headed towards\nthe Mountain in the Realm of Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:26.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's supposed to be a gate there
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:28.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that leads to the border between\nthis world and the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:30.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Mountain in the Realm of Fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:32.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this, Kagura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:34.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why have you come to\ntell us this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:35.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:37.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'd have to ask Hakudoshi that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:44.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:47.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that a message from\NHakudoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:49.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It could be a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:51.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Even if it is a {\i1}trap....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:53.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, Master Inuyasha!\NYou must not go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:55.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Mountain in the Realm of Fire\nis much too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:58.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is one place you must\nnot go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:01.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Judging from your reaction,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:05.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess this thing about a gate\nis no lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:07.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Err....no....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:09.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then we have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:13.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Regardless of what that\NHakudoshi has planned for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:44.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is turning out to be\nquite entertaining.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:50.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha, I shall let you pass\nthrough the gate first...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:54.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}in exchange for your life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.10,0:23:48.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The gate at the Realm of Fire is\nthe border between this life and the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.63,0:23:50.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The statues that we find\nthere begin to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.07,0:23:52.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They are Mezu and Gozu,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.87,0:23:54.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the gatekeepers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.40,0:23:56.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They allow only the dead to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.81,0:23:59.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They shall slay all those\nwho wish to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.84,0:24:02.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...?! My Wind Scar won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.41,0:24:04.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Blades of this world have\nno effect on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:09.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Bizarre Guards at the Border\nof the Afterlife"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.32,0:24:12.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll die and the gate\nwill open.
